description: Maki Kawasaki is the head of Team Warrior. She received the cases from the top brass and deploys the rest of the team. Maki is serious most of the time (don`t cross her when she`s serious), but she does have a sense of humor, too. She also seems to have a way of pushing the right buttons. At least, Team Warrior doesn`t seem to have much of a problem when it comes to favors (especially money).
name: Kawasaki Maki
